The anger of Americans, once they figure out what’s being done to them right now, is going to be volcanic.
The corporate-managerial-legal class that operates the Democratic Party fears anger and sees it as illegitimate as the basis for action.
If the Democrats refuse to harness the legitimate rage of Americans and direct it at those responsible for our predicament, the right will make this anger its own and will win.
Blue 2021The Democratic candidate — likely Joe Biden, but we know anything can happen in U.S. politics — beat Donald Trump going away.
But it’s going to be one or the other: The right or the left will emerge as the champion of the coming American rage.